Rockwell, Jr.  blog/hear-roger-stone-jn-ft-worth/ \nIt won’t be the shoot-out at the non-OK corral, but rather a hot, fun discussion on the election and politics at the Mises Circle , Sat., Nov. 5, 2016. Jeff Deist and Bob Murphy will also speak, and it’s just $40 per person, with a nice lunch included. Get the inside dope on the inside dopes. PS: students are free. 12:08 pm on October 26, 2016'
